    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "## Steps to reproduce\nAfter https://github.com/neovim/neovim/commit/d5516daf121aa718e79bcd423ee24c24492893c0,\n`:restart` can change the bg color:\n```\nkitty -c NONE -o 'background=#777777' env nvim --clean\n```\n\n## Expected behavior\n`restart` shouldn't change bg color\n\n## System info\n\n- Nvim version (nvim -v): `v0.12.0-dev-2725 gd5516daf12` neovim/neovim@d5516daf12\n- Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?: ?\n- Operating system/version: Linux 6.19.9-zen1-1-zen\n- Terminal name/version: kitty\n- $TERM environment variable: `xterm-kitty`\n- Installation: ?\n\n",
