        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I assume this is the same root cause for why 'termguicolors' is disabled after `:restart`. This is a known / expected regression. We'll just have to live with it temporarily, and hopefully fix it after 0.12 release.\n\nI assume this has something to do with the server not being able to see the client tty.",
