        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Related [#29634](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/29634)\n\nActually this is a bit different. What is needed here is wait for first UI to attach on non-stdio channel even if `--listen` isn't passed.\n\nCurrently, when passing `--embed` without `--headless` or `--listen`, Nvim only waits for UI on stdio channel. Perhaps this can be changed without adding an extra flag?",
            "created_at": "2026-03-29T21:03:56Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/38545#issuecomment-4151086970",
            "id": 4151086970,
